text:
@麻辣隔壁的星星
尸位素食论是202情书的王子所提出来的，当年他和作者包咪咪有多火我相信紫宸会告诉你的，结果这二人又如何？还不是因为当了权限狗而导致招致公愤？
你想当基督狗要当全世界的father，我是不是要说，基督徒都是山寨佛屎的存在？你觉得在这吧，你想冒充神父，几个人会答应？

"His Providence guides all things toward their divinely predetermined end."
Wow, no room for free will or sin in your world? And here I thought we were free agents, choosing to co-create the kingdom of God, or to refuse (to our own detriment) to follow that call 

BTW, surely you know that "predetermined" is a rejected concept attributed to certain Protestant sects. Now there is a very great deal in the reformation that Catholicism would be very wise to adopt, but me thinks you have jumped on the wrong bandwagon, R&R. ;-}

